    <item>
      <title>新西兰住房建筑成本十多年来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/new-zealand-home-building-costs-post-first-drop-in-over-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰房屋建筑成本至少 12 年来首次下降，主要原因是供应链中断缓解导致材料成本下降，以及利率上升导致需求减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/new-zealand-home-building-costs-post-first-drop-in-over-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 12:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
